{"tid":1171152,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"盧偉聰：正透過國際刑警確認消息","createTime":"2019-05-25T13:31:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T13:31:40.000Z","uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"637a9be8c36483a0e071f82033f54e6e235912c9","tid":1171152,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:31:28.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】對於德國向黃台仰及李東昇批出難民庇護，警務處處長盧偉聰表示，正透過國際刑警確認消息，視乎對方回應再決定如何跟進。<br />\n<br />\n盧偉聰又主動提到修訂逃犯條例，他舉例如有外國恐怖分子潛入香港，但現行法例有漏洞，不能將他繩之以法，對香港社會安全帶來隱憂。他希望立法會議員能集中討論如何完善條例，而非阻止條例通過。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=349290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349290&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFP2x0mEA6i1FZlyL0j1bjmE%3D&h=4be01232\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D349290&h=aa8bde18\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=349290</a>"},{"pid":"767391eee37697d7a7451bdc60e336760e0db295","tid":1171152,"uid":4783,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T13:31:40.000Z","msg":"呢班人真係完全唔識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}